data.description: Welcome to 12 Rowand Way E in Village Court neighborhood of Clementon. This gorgeous end-unit townhome was built in 2017, so everything is 5 years young. This includes all appliances, windows, roof, and HVAC. The townhome includes 3 levels of great living space. The first level has the 1 car garage, laundry, a full bath, and a first floor bedroom/bonus space. The second floor has the open concept living room, dining room, home office enclave, kitchen, and full bathroom. The top floor has the remaining 3 bedrooms, and a full bathroom. The primary bedroom has an attached 4 piece bathroom, and 2 spacious closets. Every single floor has a full bathroom, plenty of storage, for an easy low maintenance living. This home is in a great location that is easily accessible to the shore points, Philadelphia, Delaware, and other New Jersey locations. Less than 10 minutes away from grocery stores, PATCO station, Voorhees Town Center, Walmart, movie theaters, parks, and so much more! ** Best and final due by Evening of Sunday 4/17/22***
